channel.title: Final Revolution ll New Server ll need staff ll 24-7 ll join now! ll
channel.description:
Hello! Welcome to Final Revolution! We are a new server looking for players and staff! <Please dont ask!Thanks> We are currently in beta stage as i am still coding and fixing stuff. We are 24-7 And yea... Ill get on with it
Staff List Owner: Revolution
Admin - Maxpure250 Admin - Open
Mod - Open Mod - Open Mod - Open
Website/Forum: http://finalrevorsps.createaforum.com/
Webclient: Coming Soon!
Client Download: http://www.mediafire.com/?sc4ocvdz3cys5jj
Some Features of Final Revolution:
•Lots of commands that will make pking so easy for you!
•Turmoil fully working, Soul split drains enemy's prayer and increases your
health.
•Resting works and you might say how on 317 you use the command ::rest.
•If you're the type of person who likes to chill with some friends and kill
bosses, they're tons of bosses. Nomad,Corp,Kbd ETC.
•If you're competitive and you want to show off that kdr of you wrecking people
all day, there's a command ::kdr.
•Most servers off you a starter and that's all on this server home is at falador
and you get thieving stalls to make quick and faster cash!
•Don't forget to take 1 second when you log-in to look at the rules.
•Slayer task work 100% and slayer tower is available.
•You can find out the biggest updates and news with the command ::news.
•For all you people who love the idea of skilling and just want to show off all
your riches. They're skilling teleports such as ::mining ETC.
•Summoning is being coded, It's around 50% done.
•Easy training about 1 hour to get 2-3 99's.
•If you guys love to pk and don't want to lose your items there is a funpk! Yes a
funpk where you can sit there and have fun wrecking other people with your new
and expensive armor!
•Moderns,Ancients,Lunars All work!
•Hell theres even a ::chill zone! Yes a chill zone where all you do is hang with
friends and talk.
•Working 100% emotes.
Pictures:
Home: [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/zy6iz4.png[/img]
Dicing command: [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/p0fhh.png[/img]
Skill Area: [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2u7aji0.png[/img]
Boss Zone: [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/v786dc.png[/img]
